{
  "stem": "8610.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I spoke about my, my own experience. 1,700 young people came at their own expense from all over the country to New York to spend four days discussing it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had 42 workshops.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the kind of attitude and the behavior of these young people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're quite right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I did was very simple.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When it reached a crisis of, of seeing the actual situation in Belsen, I sent a circular around, certain letter, to all the Jewish personnel in the army, saying that the situation is such that I'm afraid my time must be given to them, not to you.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm sure I will get your sympathy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you can do something, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let me have your cigarette and your chocolate rations, which they did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was inundated with their chocolates and cigarettes, which I could distribute to those who were capable of using it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So nobody ever held that against me that I wasn't-- although the military authorities could very well have said, your primary job is fully-- to the army.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my Jewish conscience said, no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My responsibility is to these people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And men realized that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while they would-- created difficulties, while the military government created difficulties on one side, it sounds like they did let you do that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They couldn't stop me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It's very simple.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, I was-- the Jewish chaplain was in a very strange position.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nominally, he's responsible to his Christian superior, called the assistant chaplain general.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in fact, he's autonomous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody can tell him where to go, what to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because he does his own job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And since he's-- I'm not attached to any particular unit, but I've got the whole area at my disposal.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
